pating Chris, Rebekah and family's permanent return to Australia in December.\", \"from\": 1191, \"to\": 1296, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1233, \"end\": 1240, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rebecca\", \"score\": 0.9984759105305568, \"rank\": 0.0015264158638647414, \"text\": \"Rebekah\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rebecca\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rebecca\"}, {\"begin\": 1274, \"end\": 1283, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"score\": 0.9999883374441886, \"rank\": 1.1479019525883087e-05, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They aim to establish an equestrian centre at the Thompsons' property on Goulburn's outskirts.\", \"from\": 1297, \"to\": 1391, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1322, \"end\": 1339, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equestrianism\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.057946924217222e-17, \"text\": \"equestrian centre\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equestrianism\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equestrianism\"}, {\"begin\": 1370, \"end\": 1378, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Goulburn,_New_South_Wales\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.188645730162748e-15, \"text\": \"Goulburn\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Goulburn,_New_South_Wales\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Goulburn,_New_South_Wales\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Burton went into Monday in third position following the dressage and cross country but moved up in the ranks following the showjumping qualifying round.\", \"from\": 1393, \"to\": 1545, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Mr Thompson said his borrowed horse,Shadow Man, had captured his attention just five months ago and the pair \\\"gelled.\\\"\", \"from\": 1546, \"to\": 1664, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1549, \"end\": 1557, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tina_Thompson\", \"score\": 0.9230715078000749, \"rank\": 0.08333968873638901, \"text\": \"Thompson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tina_Thompson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tina_Thompson\"}, {\"begin\": 1582, \"end\": 1592, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trust_No_1\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.621620420556208e-19, \"text\": \"Shadow Man\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trust_No_1\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trust_No_1\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Olympian had given eventing away several years ago to concentrate on showjumping but returned in March and climbed up the rankings during numerous European competitions.\", \"from\": 1666, \"to\": 1839, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1670, \"end\": 1678, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999999980050234, \"rank\": 1.995146945609889e-09, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The silver medal adds to the team bronze he won at the Rio Olympics in 2016.\", \"from\": 1841, \"to\": 1917, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It was his third Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 1918, \"to\": 1949, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Burton is no stranger to Goulburn.\", \"from\": 1951, \"to\": 1985, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1951, \"end\": 1957, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Richard_Francis_Burton\", \"score\": 0.9655672989853932, \"rank\": 0.03548227867537499, \"text\": \"Burton\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Richard_Francis_Burton\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Richard_Francis_Burton\"}, {\"begin\": 1976, \"end\": 1984, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resou