e level but there are light years between them and him.\", \"from\": 2333, \"to\": 2413, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Chris is a very nice individual and is humble about his abilities...I am thrilled to see him win silver.\\\"\", \"from\": 2414, \"to\": 2519, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Burton, 42, grew up on a grain and cattle farm at Brymaroo, west of Toowoomba.\", \"from\": 2521, \"to\": 2599, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2521, \"end\": 2527, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Richard_Francis_Burton\", \"score\": 0.9655672989853932, \"rank\": 0.03548227867537499, \"text\": \"Burton\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Richard_Francis_Burton\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Richard_Francis_Burton\"}, {\"begin\": 2571, \"end\": 2579, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brymaroo\", \"score\": 0.9999999999918145, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Brymaroo\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brymaroo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brymaroo\"}, {\"begin\": 2589, \"end\": 2598, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Toowoomba\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2323211829469713e-14, \"text\": \"Toowoomba\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Toowoomba\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Toowoomba\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Mr Thompson speculated Chris achieved his balance from riding on the back of a motorbike with his brother, Carl, while carrying two school bags.\", \"from\": 2601, \"to\": 2745, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2604, \"end\": 2612, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tina_Thompson\", \"score\": 0.9230715078000749, \"rank\": 0.08333968873638901, \"text\": \"Thompson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tina_Thompson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tina_Thompson\"}]}, {